snippet.title: Baby Felix's Activity Center (PC Gameplay)
snippet.description:
"Baby Felix's Activity Center” is a collection of arts, crafts, music and games for children (several of which are printable) featuring characters from the "Baby Felix" series such as Baby Felix, Baby Kitty, Mookie and others. It was released in 2001 in Europe by Light and Shadow Production (LSP) and GameStory.
The character, Baby Felix, is Felix the Cat as a young and mischievous kitten. He starred in his own TV anime series, produced by Don Oriolo, called "Baby Felix and Friends" which aired from 2000-2001.
